# Tasks: Tab Manager Refactoring

**Input**: Design documents from `/specs/001-tab-manager/`
**Prerequisites**: plan.md, spec.md, research.md, data-model.md, contracts/tab-manager-api.md, quickstart.md

**Tests**: Tests are included based on existing test structure (unit/, integration/, contract/)

**Organization**: Tasks are grouped by user story to enable independent implementation and testing of each story.

## Format: `[ID] [P?] [Story] Description`

- **[P]**: Can run in parallel (different files, no dependencies)
- **[Story]**: Which user story this task belongs to (e.g., US1, US2, US3)
- Include exact file paths in descriptions

## Path Conventions

Chrome Extension architecture with TypeScript + Svelte:
- Source: `src/` at repository root
- Tests: `tests/` mirroring source structure
- Structure: `src/core/`, `src/sidepanel/`, `src/tools/`, `src/background/`, `tests/unit/`, `tests/integration/`, `tests/contract/`

---

