## Phase 2: Foundational (Core TabManager Capabilities)

**Purpose**: Merge TabGroupManager into TabManager and establish service worker initialization

This phase consolidates tab group management into TabManager and ensures proper initialization at the service worker level. These changes are required before any user story can leverage the refactored TabManager.

**⚠️ CRITICAL**: All user story work depends on this phase completing successfully

### Merge TabGroupManager into TabManager

- [ ] T014 [P] Copy groupId, groupTitle, groupColor fields from src/tools/tab/TabGroupManager.ts to src/core/TabManager.ts as private properties
- [ ] T015 [P] Copy ensureBrowserXGroup() method from TabGroupManager to TabManager as private async method
- [ ] T016 [P] Copy createBrowserXGroup() method from TabGroupManager to TabManager as private async method
- [ ] T017 [P] Copy isTabInNormalWindow() method from TabGroupManager to TabManager as private async method
- [ ] T018 [P] Copy ensureTabInNormalWindow() method from TabGroupManager to TabManager as private async method
- [ ] T019 [P] Copy moveTabToWindow() method from TabGroupManager to TabManager as private async method
- [ ] T020 Update TabManager.initialize() to call ensureBrowserXGroup() after event listener setup in src/core/TabManager.ts
- [ ] T021 Update TabManager.bindTabToSession() to add tab to group via chrome.tabs.group() in src/core/TabManager.ts
- [ ] T022 Add createAndBindTab(sessionId, options) method to TabManager in src/core/TabManager.ts that calls chrome.tabs.create() and bindTabToSession()

### Update Tests for Merged Functionality

- [ ] T023 [P] Add tab grouping verification tests to tests/unit/TabManager.test.ts (verify bindTabToSession adds to group)
- [ ] T024 [P] Add createAndBindTab() tests to tests/unit/TabManager.test.ts (verify tab creation with about:blank)
- [ ] T025 [P] Merge relevant test cases from tests/unit/TabGroupManager.test.ts into tests/unit/TabManager.test.ts
- [ ] T026 Delete tests/unit/TabGroupManager.test.ts file

### Service Worker Initialization

- [ ] T027 Add TabManager.getInstance().initialize() call to src/background/service-worker.ts global scope
- [ ] T028 Add TabManager initialization to chrome.runtime.onInstalled listener in src/background/service-worker.ts
- [ ] T029 Remove TabManager initialization from BrowserxAgent.initialize() in src/core/BrowserxAgent.ts (now done in service worker)
- [ ] T030 Update BrowserxAgent.setupTabClosureHandler() to import TabManager dynamically and register onTabClosed callback in src/core/BrowserxAgent.ts

### Cleanup

- [ ] T031 [P] Remove all TabGroupManager imports from codebase (grep and replace)
- [ ] T032 Delete src/tools/tab/TabGroupManager.ts file
- [ ] T033 Verify all tests pass after merge: npm test
- [ ] T034 Verify TypeScript compilation passes: npm run type-check

**Checkpoint**: TabManager fully consolidated with grouping, service worker initialization complete, all tests passing

