## Phase 5: User Story 5 - Service Worker Level Initialization (Priority: P3)

**Goal**: TabManager initialized at service worker level, ensuring state persists across agent lifecycles and multiple sessions share infrastructure

**Why out of sequence**: This was completed in Phase 2 (T027-T030) as a foundational requirement. This phase documents verification and any remaining integration.

**Independent Test**: Initialize service worker, create multiple agent instances, verify they all share the same TabManager singleton and state.

### Verification for User Story 5

- [ ] T055 [US5] Verify TabManager singleton behavior across multiple agent instances in tests/integration/session-tab-lifecycle.test.ts
- [ ] T056 [US5] Add test for TabManager state persistence across agent termination/recreation in tests/unit/TabManager.test.ts
- [ ] T057 [US5] Add test for concurrent sessions with different tab bindings in tests/integration/concurrent-binding.test.ts
- [ ] T058 [US5] Verify service worker initialization logs TabManager initialization message when extension loads
- [ ] T059 [US5] Verify all User Story 5 tests pass: npm test

**Checkpoint**: User Story 5 verified - service worker initialization working, singleton pattern confirmed

